original_title: SF participates in SJB working committee
original_body_lines: Colombo, March 20 (Daily Mirror) - Samagi Jana Balawegaya (SJB) Chairman Sarath Fonseka participated in the party's working committee meeting.
Party sources said Field Marshal Fonseka did not speak but only listened to others.
Fonseka obtained a stay order from the Supreme Courts against his suspension from the SJB recently.
